text: Abdelmoumen Sifour (; born March 3, 1998) is an Algerian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for USM Alger in the Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1. ==Club career== In 2019, Abdelmoumen Sifour was promoted to USM Alger's first team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:People from Algiers Category:Algerian footballers Category:Living people Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:USM Alger players
